OL,3,CPrince William called 'best Papa in
OL,4,Cthe world' as family mark his 44th
OL,5,Cbirthday
OL,7,FThe Prince of Wales marked his 44th
OL,8,Fbirthday and Father's Day, coinciding
OL,9,Fwith a photograph of him with his
OL,10,Fdaughter Princess Charlotte after
OL,11,FTrooping the Colour.
OL,13,FThe photograph was shared by
OL,14,FKensington Palace on Instagram on
OL,15,FWilliam's birthday on Sunday with the
OL,16,Fcaption: "Happy birthday and Father's
OL,17,FDay to the best Papa in the World! We
OL,18,Flove you very much. C, G, C & L" and
OL,19,Fan emoji of two pink hearts.
OL,26,@xD@JOUzD@`O]
