OL,3,CPrince William called 'best Papa in
OL,4,Cthe world' as family mark his 44th
OL,5,Cbirthday
OL,7,FThe family were at the Trooping the
OL,8,FColour last weekend and the picture
OL,9,Fshared on social media was taken in
OL,10,Fthe garden of Kensington Palace after
OL,11,Fthe ceremony, with William in the
OL,12,Fscarlet dress uniform of the Welsh
OL,13,FGuards, of which he is colonel, and
OL,14,FCharlotte in a cream dress.
OL,16,FIn his birthday week, the Prince of
OL,17,FWales was joined by his wife at Royal
OL,18,FAscot for the first time since 2023.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
