OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782061560
OL,3,CPrince William called 'best Papa in
OL,4,Cthe world' as family mark his 44th
OL,5,Cbirthday
OL,7,FOn Wednesday, Kate and William took
OL,8,Fpart in the traditional carriage ride,
OL,9,Fenjoyed the races from the royal box
OL,10,Fand even shared a joke with former
OL,11,FEngland manager Sir Gareth Southgate
OL,12,Fbefore the World Cup match against
OL,13,FCroatia.
OL,15,FThe princess made her first appearance
OL,16,Fat the famous Berkshire meet since
OL,17,Fbeing diagnosed with cancer in early
OL,18,F2024 and later undergoing successful
OL,19,Fchemotherapy treatment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
