OL,3,CPrince William called 'best Papa in
OL,4,Cthe world' as family mark his 44th
OL,5,Cbirthday
OL,7,FThe couple were also part of Monday's
OL,8,FGarter Day celebrations at Windsor
OL,9,FCastle.
OL,11,FBut it appears to be a quieter
OL,12,Fbirthday for the prince than in 2024,
OL,13,Fwhen he took Prince George and
OL,14,FPrincess Charlotte to see Taylor Swift
OL,15,Fat Wembley Stadium.
